spec_data.Name: perl-ExtUtils-Depends
spec_data.Description:
This module tries to make it easy to build Perl extensions that use
functions and typemaps provided by other Perl extensions. This means
that a Perl extension is treated like a shared library that provides
also a C and an XS interface besides the Perl one.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:25:11 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Easily build XS extensions that depend on XS extensions
